<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>This application is a reporting file created for the standard variation margin calculation routine supplied with T24.</p>
            <p> A DX.RV.DET. . .HIST file exists for every DX.MARGIN.CALC record that has been created. </p>
            <p> This files are used for historical storage of revaluation details.</p>
            <p> They share there file layout with the DX.REVAL.DET. . . for the DX.MARGIN.CALC record.</p>
            <p> Validation Rules</p>
            <p />
            <p> None</p>
        </ovdesc>
